== 交通 ==

境內交通方便，陸上交通有四通八達的公路和鐵路。鐵路全長4787公里<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.cia.gov/library/publications/the-world-factbook/rankorder/2121rank.html?countryName=Mozambique&countryCode=mz&regionCode=af&rank=37#mz|title=中央情報局世界概況--鐵路|access-date=2010-08-06|archive-date=2020-11-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201128095143/https://www.cia.gov/library/publications/the-world-factbook/rankorder/2121rank.html?countryName=Mozambique&countryCode=mz&regionCode=af&rank=37#mz|dead-url=no}}</ref>，可以和南非共和國、史瓦濟蘭、辛巴威和馬拉威等地鐵路相接。公路全長30,400公里<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.cia.gov/library/publications/the-world-factbook/rankorder/2085rank.html?countryName=Mozambique&countryCode=mz&regionCode=af&rank=97#mz|title=中央情報局世界概況--公路|access-date=2010-08-06|archive-date=2020-11-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201129051922/https://www.cia.gov/library/publications/the-world-factbook/rankorder/2085rank.html?countryName=Mozambique&countryCode=mz&regionCode=af&rank=97#mz|dead-url=no}}</ref>，其中五分之二是柏油路面，五分之三是大級路面<ref>改寫自《非洲列國誌》--莫桑比克，頁338,1981年出版</ref>。航空交通有國營的莫三比克航空公司和一些外國航空公司的民航班機，營運國內外航線海運最為發達，這裡良好的港口可以和世界各大港口通航。國內主要港口有[[馬布多|馬布多]]、[[貝拉|貝拉]]、[[南普拉|南普拉]]和[[貴利曼納|貴利曼納]]等。

== 國際貿易 ==
=== 出口貿易 ===
在出口貿易方面，2009年輸出總值約為19.65億美元<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.cia.gov/library/publications/the-world-factbook/rankorder/2078rank.html?countryName=Mozambique&countryCode=mz&regionCode=af&rank=128#mz|title=中央情報局世界概況--出口總值|access-date=2010-08-06|archive-date=2020-09-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200919150010/https://www.cia.gov/library/publications/the-world-factbook/rankorder/2078rank.html?countryName=Mozambique&countryCode=mz&regionCode=af&rank=128#mz|dead-url=no}}</ref>，主要輸出品有鋁、大蝦、腰果、棉花、糖、柑橘、木材、電力設備等<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.cia.gov/library/publications/the-world-factbook/fields/2049.html?countryName=Mozambique&countryCode=mz&regionCode=af&#mz|title=中央情報局世界概況--出口商品|access-date=2010-08-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100424194154/https://www.cia.gov/library/publications/the-world-factbook/fields/2049.html?countryName=Mozambique&countryCode=mz&regionCode=af&#mz|archive-date=2010-04-24|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，主要輸出國為[[荷蘭|荷蘭]]、[[南非|南非]]及[[辛巴威|辛巴威]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.cia.gov/library/publications/the-world-factbook/fields/2050.html?countryName=Angola&countryCode=ao&regionCode=af&#ao|title=中央情報局世界概況--出口貿易國|access-date=2010-08-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100425122236/https://www.cia.gov/library/publications/the-world-factbook/fields/2050.html?countryName=Angola&countryCode=ao&regionCode=af&#ao|archive-date=2010-04-25|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

=== 進口貿易 ===
在進口貿易方面，2009年輸入總值約為30.96億美元<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.cia.gov/library/publications/the-world-factbook/rankorder/2087rank.html?countryName=Angola&countryCode=ao&regionCode=af&rank=76#ao|title=中央情報局世界概況--進口總值|access-date=2010-08-06|archive-date=2020-12-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201212120000/https://www.cia.gov/library/publications/the-world-factbook/rankorder/2087rank.html?countryName=Angola&countryCode=ao&regionCode=af&rank=76#ao|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，主要輸入品有機械及設備、車輛、燃料、化學品、金屬製品、食品、紡織品等<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.cia.gov/library/publications/the-world-factbook/fields/2058.html?countryName=Mozambique&countryCode=mz&regionCode=af&#mz|title=中央情報局世界概況--進口商品|access-date=2010-08-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100424194541/https://www.cia.gov/library/publications/the-world-factbook/fields/2058.html?countryName=Mozambique&countryCode=mz&regionCode=af&#mz|archive-date=2010-04-24|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。主要輸入國是南非、荷蘭及[[中國|中國]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.cia.gov/library/publications/the-world-factbook/fields/2061.html?countryName=Mozambique&countryCode=mz&regionCode=af&#mz|title=中央情報局世界概況--進口貿易國|access-date=2010-08-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100424194407/https://www.cia.gov/library/publications/the-world-factbook/fields/2061.html?countryName=Mozambique&countryCode=mz&regionCode=af&#mz|archive-date=2010-04-24|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

